\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And were the clothes that you had new or second hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh no, they were new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Always new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And where were they bought, what kind of place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Well usually round about there were some good sh
ops those days. I remember we had to go to a very good boot shop, and my beautiful boots when I was a child. I always remember that. Lovely patent leather - boots they were. They were lovely with buttons to. They were very meticulous.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Was this a small shop or was it a big shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No it was a small one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Small local shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes, small local shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And would you have bought your clothes here as well, this sort of shop, not in the boot shop obviously.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh no. There was another shop in the same neighbourhood that used to sell clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 A smaller shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes comparatively small.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now when would you have bought new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh whenever we needed them. My mother kept us very well dressed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 There wasn't any particular time in the year when you had something new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And what about shoes? When did you buy new shoes? Were the shoes always new, incidentally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh always, yes. She never bought anything second hand, my mother, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And were these bought - the shoes - just when they were needed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Not any particular time of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Just when one pair wore out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Sometimes on a Saturday night she used to take me out, I remember, to a shop in what used to be called \{BLANK\}
 and to tell you the truth they used to have checks those days, and they were very handy for people that hadn't got a lot of money, you know, not like these affluent days. So I remember that very well. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No she wouldn't let him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Did he do anything? Any cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No, he was always reading. A great reader. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Cooking, washing up, cleaning fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No he didn't. He wasn't a domesticated man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 What about decorating or repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh no. Oh no. They used to come in to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 He wouldn't make any improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 I don't think he bothered much as long as it was all right. My mother'd see to all that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 She was the one who saw to things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now did he ever dress or undress you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Bath you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Or read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now read, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 He did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And did he tell you stories.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes. Not exact
ly stories, but he'd tell me, he'd ask me what a certain word meant. And he did say to me once, 'If anybody ever asks you where you came from tell them that you belong to the Fosters of \{BLANK\}
 in County Kildare.' I always remember him telling me that. But I've never seen Ireland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Haven't you. Oh it's just a sort of name. Well it's a lovely country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 I've been to Scotland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And that's another lovely country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 I loved Scotland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now did he ever take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Quite often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 
He used to take me every Sunday morning, myself and little cousin, same age as myself, and he used to take us down to the docks. He had a brother on one of the ships and he used to take us. I used to love going down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 This was a regular thing was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes, on a Sunday morning.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 But this was the only occasion that he took you out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh that's the only one I remember yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now did he ever look after you when your mother was out?
