\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home at help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No. Only go messages and ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No particular jobs that it was thing to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 I don't remember. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And you used to go messages?
