\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Up 'til the time you left school, but you didn't continue after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And what about your sisters, did they have any regular jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes they had. My eldest sister she worked in a ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No I mean in the home, any jobs to help your parents?
