ar as I can remember, but he was very fond of, I don't suppose you've ever had it, real Liverpool, salt fish he was fond of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh I've heard a lot of people mention that. It seems to be a most popular dish in those days.
