\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 No. I liked it too. I liked the salt fish.
