Well my father was a great reader, and he used to go out a little bit. On a Sunday he used to go out a bit for walks and round and about. And my mother, well she didn't have much spare time. And what spa
re time she had, on a weekday she'd do a bit of sewing, whatever was wanted in the house, and well Sunday she used to go to church. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now, did your mother ...
