\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 I was just going to ask you did your mother have any interests outside the home, apart from church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes, she used to like the \{BLANK\} one near where you had a concert hall. They had lovely concerts there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 So she used to go to these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 She used to go, yes. All used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Would they be in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 In the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Sometimes on a Monday evening, and it was only a penny. Penny concert and they were lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 What kind of concerts were they? Sort of musical?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Instrumental or singing as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Yes. Yes. Oh lovely singing. Really lovely concerts they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 And would she go to these quite often or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13859573 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Well nearly every Monday night we used to go, as far as I can remember.
