\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16541165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12453023\charrsid10692593 Now did she ever go out to enjoy herself apart from that?
